# Custom Fonts Guide

Custom fonts are stored in the [app/fonts/](mdc:app/fonts) directory:

- [GeistVF.woff](mdc:app/fonts/GeistVF.woff): Geist Sans variable font.
- [GeistMonoVF.woff](mdc:app/fonts/GeistMonoVF.woff): Geist Mono variable font.

These fonts are loaded and configured in [layout.tsx](mdc:app/layout.tsx) using `next/font/local`, and applied globally via CSS variables for consistent typography across the app.
